00:56:42,260 --> 00:56:43,280
[SPEAKER_01] biti ponosni

764
00:56:43,280 --> 00:56:44,800
[SPEAKER_01] na žrtvu koju su podnijeli.

765
00:56:44,800 --> 00:56:46,519
[SPEAKER_01] Jer moramo graditi to jedno

766
00:56:46,519 --> 00:56:50,639
[SPEAKER_01] kulturalno i multicivilizacijsko društvo,

767
00:56:50,639 --> 00:56:53,199
[SPEAKER_01] jer granice Hrvatske će biti otvorene.

768
00:56:53,199 --> 00:56:54,519
