772
00:56:58,780 --> 00:57:00,239
[SPEAKER_01] Pa meni su nedavno u ulici

773
00:57:00,239 --> 00:57:01,960
[SPEAKER_01] dečki Filipinci

774
00:57:01,960 --> 00:57:03,719
[SPEAKER_01] kopali za optički kabel.

775
00:57:03,719 --> 00:57:05,320
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam im donio dvije pive.

776
00:57:05,320 --> 00:57:06,699
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su bili oduševljeni.

777
00:57:06,699 --> 00:57:07,539
[SPEAKER_01] Joj, brother,

778
00:57:07,920 --> 00:57:09,840
[SPEAKER_01] valih nitko jadne nije abadirao,

779
00:57:09,840 --> 00:57:10,380
[SPEAKER_01] razumijete,

780
00:57:10,380 --> 00:57:11,920
[SPEAKER_01] na kojem jeziku komunicirati.

781
00:57:11,920 --> 00:57:13,340
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, nažalost, Hrvatska ostaje

782
00:57:13,340 --> 00:57:15,039
[SPEAKER_01] bez ljudi,

783
00:57:15,039 --> 00:57:15,639
[SPEAKER_01] razumijete,

784
