[SPEAKER_01] s čemu i ljudi će dolaziti raditi.

786
00:57:18,280 --> 00:57:19,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ovdje, de facto,

787
00:57:19,420 --> 00:57:20,900
[SPEAKER_01] mi moramo samo stvoriti

788
00:57:20,900 --> 00:57:22,519
