797
00:57:37,619 --> 00:57:39,159
[SPEAKER_00] Da pripremimo javnost,

798
00:57:39,159 --> 00:57:41,380
[SPEAKER_01] da ih doista ne diskriminira.

799
00:57:41,380 --> 00:57:43,860
[SPEAKER_01] A to što ona po javnošću

